From,their,site,LetsProve,is,an,online,life,stream,service,which,helps,you,to,keep,up,to,date,on,activities,that,your,friends,and,family,are,doing,Any,activities,like,blogging,photos,reading,news,etc,Add,some,applications,and,share,your,activities,with,your,friends,LetsProve,s,Platform,enables,anyone,to,build,applications,that,can,update,your,activities,from,external,services,and,send,notifications,Choose,useful,and,relevant,applications,to,show,your,identity,and,experience,to,the,world